Label every lattice point by its coordinates  
(x , y) with the origin at 1, the x-axis pointing to the right and the y-axis
pointing downward.  
On the square spiral

• the point (0,0) carries 1;  
• the spiral winds counter-clockwise;  
• the point (r , r) (bottom-right corner of the square with radius r)
carries the largest number in the ring,  
 M(r)= (2r+1)² ;  
• the four corners of that ring are  
 SE : M(r) at ( r ,  r)  
 SW : M(r)−2r at (−r ,  r)  
 NW : M(r)−4r at (−r ,−r)  
 NE : M(r)−6r at ( r ,−r).

Between two corners the numbers change by 1 along the side.

------------------------------------------------
1. Locate 2026
------------------------------------------------
(2·22+1)² = 45² = 2025 < 2026 ≤ (2·23+1)² = 47² = 2209,  
hence 2026 lies in ring r = 23.  
Because every new ring starts one step to the right of the
previous South-East corner, 2026 is at

(23 , 22).

------------------------------------------------
2. Find the eight neighbouring coordinates
------------------------------------------------
(22,21)  (23,21)  (24,21)  
(22,22)  (23,22)  (24,22)  
(22,23)  (23,23)  (24,23)

(the middle one (23,22) is 2026 itself).

------------------------------------------------
3. Evaluate each neighbour
------------------------------------------------
A coordinate (x , y) belongs to ring r = max(|x| ,|y|).
Put P(r) = (2r−1)² = largest number of the previous ring.

Right side (x = r, y ≤ r−1): value = P(r)+1 + (r−1−y)  
Bottom side (y = r, x ≤ r−1): value = M(r) − (r−x)

Applying these rules:

(22,21): r=22, right side, value = 1849+1+0 = 1850  
(23,21): r=23, right side, value = 2025+1+1 = 2027  
(24,21): r=24, right side, value = 2209+1+2 = 2212  

(22,22): r=22, SE corner, value = 2025  
(24,22): r=24, right side, value = 2209+1+1 = 2211  

(22,23): r=23, bottom side, value = 2209−1 = 2208  
(23,23): r=23, SE corner, value = 2209  
(24,23): r=24, first cell of ring 24, value = 2209+1 = 2210

------------------------------------------------
4. Sum
------------------------------------------------
1850 + 2027 + 2212 + 2025 + 2211 + 2208 + 2209 + 2210
= 16 952

------------------------------------------------
Answer
------------------------------------------------
The sum of the eight neighbours of 2026 is 16 952.
